data.description: Charming rear dormer cape on spacious property with a blend of stone and brick exterior that is timeless. The Main Floor has 2 nice sized bedrooms, 1 Full Bath,Updated kitchen with granite counter tops, Formal Dining room,Hardwood floors and a cozy fireplace, A Breezeway to the attached garage, On the 2nd floor there are and 2 bedrooms with 1 full bath and a nice size den/living space.  Skylight for extra sunshine, 2nd floor terrace. Lots of living space, plenty of room for family members and guests. Lots of storage in the basement. Large fenced in yard well manicured and beautifully landscaped.
